Class PlaylistController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.ui.commons.controller.custom.InstantiableReinitializableSplitControllerView

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PlaylistProvider, PlayableSongProvider, PlayableSongQueueProvider, SongListProvider, SongProvider, SongSelectionProvider, SongViewer, CloseableControllerHandler, InstantiableController, InstantiableControllerView, InstantiableReinitializableControllerView, Reinitializable

    public class PlaylistController
extends SongsController
implements PlaylistProvider
    A custom type of SongsController that instead of view a song when a row is double clicked plays it (actually notifies the delegate about the fact which should play it).
